text: Wonder Wheel is a 2017 American period drama movie directed by Woody Allen and starring Kate Winslet, Juno Temple, Justin Timberlake, Jim Belushi, Tony Sirico, Debi Mazar, Thomas Guiry. It was distributed by Amazon Studios. ==Other websites== * * Category:2017 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Woody Allen
